NOTE ON MODEL WEIGHTS

This repository contains code for fine-tuning and serving Google's Gemma 4
model. The model weights themselves are licensed separately by Google under
the Gemma Terms of Use. Users must accept those terms at
https://ai.google.dev/gemma/terms before downloading or using the weights.
